## kebab-case

- Files and Folders

```
product-card.tsx
add-to-cart-button.tsx
use-cart.ts
```

## PascalCase

- React Components (Pages, Components)

```
export function ProductCard() {}
```

## camelCase

- Functions and Variables

```
getProductList
handleSubmit
```

## UPPER_SNAKE_CASE

- Constants

```
MAX_CART_ITEMS
API_BASE_URL
```
